data.description: Nestled in Cherokee Station, this stunning family home offers a perfect blend of style and comfort. The spacious residence boasts beautiful wood laminate flooring throughout the first floor, creating an inviting and low-maintenance living environment. The elegant foyer leads to a formal dining room with decorative wainscoting and a cozy living room or office space. The heart of the home unfolds in the family room, which features a gas fireplace, making it a perfect gathering place. The adjacent kitchen is a chef's dream, showcasing an island, granite countertops, rich espresso finish cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances, including a wall oven. The triple windows in the kitchen provide a delightful view of the large, privately fenced backyard, ensuring your space is serene and secluded. Upstairs, all bedrooms offer ample walk-in closet space, with the Primary Suite being a true highlight. It features a sitting area and has two walk-in closets. The Primary Bedroom is equally impressive, with espresso finish cabinetry, granite countertops, double sink vanity, separate shower, and a relaxing garden tub. A separate laundry room adds convenience to your daily routine. The exterior of the property is equally charming, with a white vinyl fence, sodded yards in the front and back, an irrigation system, and a 2-car garage. Don't miss the opportunity to call 433 Meloney Drive your new home; it's a true gem in Hinesville. [Grass enhanced in some photos]
